    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾姆柏醒来，迅速发现自己身处地狱。这是一款 roguelite 射击游戏，会让你开心到在父亲身上喷洒满满的快乐与“恶心”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/477c71a82109a33e34fd911d7cba4c4e.webp?t=1772168886\" width=616 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/44231d129aea63fd094b73939a3d0648.poster.avif?t=1772168886\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/44231d129aea63fd094b73939a3d0648.webm?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/44231d129aea63fd094b73939a3d0648.mp4?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>坠入血淋淋的、受经典恐怖片启发的地狱密室：这里充满了脉动的血腥、强烈的视觉冲击，简直让人恶心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/31b031e1efa910f1425fc6b266e4f509.webp?t=1772168886\" width=616 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/8825faba1fe1d3f48b47071519f6a529.poster.avif?t=1772168886\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/8825faba1fe1d3f48b47071519f6a529.webm?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/8825faba1fe1d3f48b47071519f6a529.mp4?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>用艾姆柏的链锯枪和其他暴力又搞笑的武器，将这受诅咒的地狱屠杀成一片片血海。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/e267e9846215ff03d971cf0095f4ec4b.webp?t=1772168886\" width=616 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/bc197eb5d2c1f5cc71fc03b2343820af.poster.avif?t=1772168886\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/bc197eb5d2c1f5cc71fc03b2343820af.webm?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/bc197eb5d2c1f5cc71fc03b2343820af.mp4?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>用受诅咒的物品升级炸弹和武器，同时提升自己的技能，努力打通逃出地狱的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/b09a716c22ba36616ea2adbd887ae764.webp?t=1772168886\" width=616 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/f304410699617533c70c22983aa04d60.poster.avif?t=1772168886\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/f304410699617533c70c22983aa04d60.webm?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/f304410699617533c70c22983aa04d60.mp4?t=1772168886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>消灭恶心的首领，披上他们的内脏，揭开艾姆柏的过去和现实未来的真相，同时保持外表的酷炫与可爱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217880/extras/cf41d3d6182ecec2ba384521dd0e913f.webp?t=1772168886\" width=616 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专属血腥引擎<br>随机生成的地牢<br>各种枪械<br>数百种升级和协同装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成群的敌人类型<br>无数首领<br>双摇杆射击玩法<br>roguelite游戏机制<br>可收集的贴纸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精神恢复套餐<br>混乱家庭套餐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到我们Steam页面的本地化版本；我们希望您享受用您自己语言了解关于我们游戏信息的过程！关于最终游戏的本地化，我们尚未做出决定，这将取决于各个地区的愿望单数量。如果您希望看到这款游戏以您的语言呈现，请分享这个消息，帮助我们在您的地区获得足够的愿望单以支持本地化！</p>",
